==================================================
EXPERIENCE MATCHING ENGINE
==================================================

The platform should compare:
- contract maturity
- user/company maturity

The goal is to:
- maximize realistic wins
- reduce wasted proposal effort
- reduce operational failure
- avoid impossible pursuits

==================================================
IMPORTANT PRODUCT DIFFERENTIATOR
==================================================

Most procurement tools assume:
“Find opportunity → submit bid.”

GovSignal AI should determine:
“Does this company realistically have the maturity, partnerships, and operational structure to execute successfully?”

==================================================
PLATFORM GOAL
==================================================

The platform should:
- guide realistic growth
- identify solvable gaps
- identify dangerous gaps
- encourage strategic progression
- reduce low-probability bidding
- improve operational decision-making

==================================================
FINAL PLATFORM PHILOSOPHY
==================================================

The platform is NOT intended to:
- encourage reckless bidding
- encourage operational overextension
- treat all opportunities equally

The platform IS intended to:
- intelligently evaluate opportunity realism
- guide strategic company growth
- identify partnership opportunities
- identify capability gaps
- improve execution feasibility
- maximize realistic contract success

The platform should function as:
“AI-assisted procurement maturity and execution intelligence”